## Summary

Airbrush integration is primarily **off-chain and data-driven**, requiring conformance to a published schema (OpenAPI YAML/JSON) and usage of the provided Python document tooling. There are **no Solidity contracts, proxy/initializer patterns, event hooks, or blockchain network requirements** within this repository. Integrators wishing to bridge Airbrush into on-chain workflows must map its data structures appropriately and manage all blockchain/contract-related concerns externally.

For further detail or to ensure up-to-date best practices, refer to the linked files and contact airbrush@originmarkets.com.
